  "title": "Education Centre Admin Coordinator [ With relevant exp / 3 days office 2 days WFH ] 7094",
  "description": "<p>Working location: Tiong Bahru<br />Working days: </p><ul><li>3 days Office (Weekdays) 10.20am - 7.20pm </li><li>2 days WFH (Weekend) 7.00am – 5pm</li></ul><p>Industry: Education centre </p><p><strong>Teachers & CSO Deployment</strong></p><ul><li>Plan and manage relief processes across branches for Teachers & Customer Service Officers -Track Attendance of Teachers & Customer Service Officers</li><li>Develop communications packages for teachers (e.g. Infographics, etc)</li><li>Design simple collaterals in accordance with brand marketing guidelines</li><li>Assist with scheduling and tracking of teacher assessments, appraisal, etc</li></ul><p><strong>Data-tracking & Manpower Resource Management</strong></p><ul><li>Plan and manage relief processes across branches for Teachers & CSOS</li><li>Oversee Teacher Allocation across all branches</li><li>Measure adherence to leave policies and implement measures to encourage adherence Manage relief data sheets</li><li>Deliver monthly report on key data points tracked by team</li></ul><p><strong>Oversee Relief Roster</strong></p><ul><li>Find relief teachers</li><li>Consolidate a list of relief, freelance relief classes taken monthly and inform HR</li></ul><p><strong>Assist with forecasting of recruitment needs of the following groups of teachers:</strong></p><ul><li>Relief, Adjunct, Part-time and Freelance</li></ul><p><strong>Data-tracking for Operations</strong></p><ul><li>Manage key data sheets for Operations needs</li><li>Deliver monthly report on key data points tracked by team</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>At least Degree / Diploma in any discipline</li><li>Possess relevant experience</li><li>Proficiency in MS Office, Zoom, Google Drive</li></ul><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>Ho Ming Jie (Edmund) Reg No: R1987094 </strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279 </strong></p>",
